    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring a 6-speed manual gearbox. This example has been meticulously maintained with a recent VANOS overhaul and documented subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The drivetrain remains tight, benefiting from a factory-spec limited-slip differential and refreshed bushings across the multi-link rear suspension. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its driver-status, the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) are perfectly synced, providing the razor-sharp throttle response this chassis is renowned for. A true driver\u2019s car with sorted internals and robust performance.",
