    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2019 Audi A6 3.0T Premium Plus offers a refined driving experience with a focus on sophisticated tech and comfort. The Mythos Black Metallic exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though it shows a few minor, expected stone chips on the hood from commute use. The Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional grip, and the engine remains responsive and smooth. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Nougat Brown leather and fine grain ash wood inlays. The leather is in great shape, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Both the upper and lower MMI touchscreens are crisp and fully operational, as is the Audi Virtual Cockpit. This vehicle has been regularly serviced at scheduled intervals, and the Continental tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. It is a well-cared-for executive sedan that balances luxury and performance perfectly.",
