      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six powerplant, utilizing its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup for linear power delivery and exceptional mid-range torque. Mated to a robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, this chassis offers precise power management. The suspension retains its four-wheel independent double-wishbone geometry, providing superior lateral stability and mechanical grip. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and fresh fluid cycles for the hydraulic braking system. It presents in honest, driver-ready condition with minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, but remains mechanically sound with excellent compression across all cylinders.",
